                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8846" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2218</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1312 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新驱动，智造未来：红豆集团的数字化转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Innovation driven, intelligent manufacturing for the future: the digital transformation of Hodo Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张爱国，崔庆海，刘倩，林香艳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">红豆集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；智能化；创新；红豆集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation;Intelligence;Innovation;Hodo Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字经济作为新时代的经济驱动力，将引领新一轮的科技革命和产业变革，推动经济的高质量发展和社会的全面进步。而“数字化转型”为各行各业带来了前所未有的机遇与挑战，它逐渐消融了数字经济与传统产业的边界。在“智改数转”的时代浪潮中，红豆集团敏锐地捕捉到了这一机遇，以坚定的步伐不断推进企业的转型升级。本案例介绍了红豆集团在祖孙三代的接力传承下跌宕起伏的发展历程，重点阐述了红豆集团将数字化转型贯穿于企业生产、销售等全流程，使企业的成本控制更精准、采购计划更科学、决策行为更理性，实现从传统制造型企业迈向数字化企业的蝶变。本案例旨在引导学生深入理解传统制造企业数字化转型的内在逻辑，掌握数字化转型的动因。也希望能给其他传统制造型企业提供可供参考的经验和启示，助力其实现数字化转型升级。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The digital economy, as a driving force in the new era, is poised to lead the next wave of technological revolutions and industrial transformations, propelling high-quality economic development and comprehensive societal progress. The concept of &quot;digital transformation&quot; presents unprecedented opportunities and challenges across various sectors, gradually erasing the boundaries between the digital economy and traditional industries. In the era marked by &quot;intelligence-driven and digital transformation,&quot; the Hodo Group has astutely seized these opportunities, steadfastly advancing its corporate transformation and upgrading. This case study recounts the turbulent development journey of the Hodo Group, passed down through three generations. It highlights how the company has integrated digital transformation into every aspect of its operations, from production to sales, enabling more precise cost control, more scientific procurement plans, and more rational decision-making. This transformation has catalyzed the metamorphosis from a traditional manufacturing enterprise to a digitally advanced company.This case study aims to guide students to deeply understand the internal logic of digital transformation in traditional manufacturing enterprises and grasp the motivations for digital transformation. It also hopes to provide available experience and inspiration for other traditional manufacturing enterprises to help them achieve digital transformation and upgrading.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；战略转型动因；数字化转型三阶段模型；价值创造；动态能力</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
